- "Whispers of the past" indicates the previous year's financial metrics;
- "Financial landscape" and "ponds reflecting their financial health" are metaphors for the companies and their financial metrics.

- 'person leading it' refers to the CEO;
- 'what financial aspect was measured' refers to the metric name, such as Revenues or Profits;
